Users who cannot administer a space cannot see the mail accounts that are used for this space. This forces us to document them manually in a page.

It would be interesting if the mail accounts would be displayed  in the Space Summary and on the Mail Archive page. A macro could also be handy to list them on a page without worrying about keeping it in synch with the config.
